query:
INSERT INTO rooms(key,tumonline_org_id,tumonline_calendar_id,tumonline_room_id,last_scrape)
            VALUES ($1,$2,$3,$4,$5)
            ON CONFLICT (key) DO UPDATE SET
              tumonline_org_id=$2,
              tumonline_calendar_id=$3,
              tumonline_room_id=$4,
              last_scrape=$5
